## Special Acknowledgement & Credits

This software was developed using **Vide Coding** techniques in collaboration with **Google Gemini 3.5 Flash with Antigravity Agent**

The project's architecture, logic, and user interface were co-authored by an Agentic AI system. This project serves as a demonstration of high-performance development powered by advanced LLMs, specifically **Gemini 1.5 Flash** during high-demand periods.

Sweep was born from a real-world developer frustration: the "1GB Disk Space" incident. It is a tribute to human-AI synergy.
